In order to prepare for their Unit Two Test- Reading and Analyzing an informative Or Literary Text; Middle School students played their own version of â€œEscape Roomâ€ in ELA.

When writing a story , itâ€™s always best to use the small moments where you learned something or realized something to develop your Personal Narrative Story.
